Serializable, BeanClassLoaderAware, BeanFactoryAware, FactoryBean, InitializingBean
public class SetOnceClassLoaderTxProxyFactoryBean
extends CurrentClassLoaderTxProxyFactoryBean

This is needed to keep the ClassLoader from getting overwritten after we set it, the ClassLoader can only be set one time using the setter method
